<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠٨٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6952">يَحْيَى بْنُ بُكَيْرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ: </a>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">ابْنُ الْمُسَيَّبِ </a>: إِنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«الْحَلِفُ مُنَفِّقَةٌ لِلسِّلْعَةِ، مُمْحِقَةٌ لِلْبَرَكَةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>